name: Jump Out South Canyon
description:
Introduction

A scenic drop into Woods Canyon with a short hike to the exit drainage

Approach

Park at one of the two car parks depending on how far you want to drive in and start your approach from there.

Descent

A scenic narrow drop into Woods Canyon consisting of a handful of rappels.

Exit

Hike down Woods Canyon a short distance to the exit drainage and follow the track back up to your vehicle.
